org.apache.ambari.server.controller.metrics

Interface MetricPropertyProviderFactory


  • public interface MetricPropertyProviderFactory
    The MetricPropertyProviderFactory is used to provide injected instances of PropertyProviders which retrieve metrics.

        Gets a Guice-inject instance of a JMXPropertyProvider.

        componentMetrics - the map of supported metrics
        streamProvider - the stream provider
        jmxHostProvider - the JMX host mapping
        metricHostProvider - the host mapping
        clusterNamePropertyId - the cluster name property id

      • createRESTMetricsPropertyProvider

        RestMetricsPropertyProvider createRESTMetricsPropertyProvider(Map<String,String> metricsProperties,

        /** Create a REST property provider.
        Parameters:
        metricsProperties - the map of per-component metrics properties
        componentMetrics - the map of supported metrics for component
        streamProvider - the stream provider
        metricHostProvider - metricsHostProvider instance
        clusterNamePropertyId - the cluster name property id
        hostNamePropertyId - the host name property id, or null if none.
        componentNamePropertyId - the component name property id
        statePropertyId - the state property id or null if none.
        componentName - the name of the component which the metric is for, or null if none.
        Returns:
        the instantiated and injected RestMetricsPropertyProvider.
